    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News April 14</title>
      <lead>The Newsletter from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI is published.</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First national High-Level Meeting of VPET Stakeholders and VPET Partner Conference&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Laying the foundations for tomorrow‘s VPET system &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6th Intercantonal VET Day&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;VET and apprenticeships the focus of 31 private radio broadcasts &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultation on core syllabus for the teaching of sports in VET programmes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Fit for the future: new basis for mandatory sports &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;National Qualifications Framework for the VPET System&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Preparatory work continues &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;"Match-Prof" project in vocational and professional education and training&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;"Win-win situation for young people and businesses" &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Move towards setting up a centre for Islam and society&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;From theory to practice &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bibliometric study on research in Switzerland 1981-2011&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Swiss research has particularly dense international networks &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exchanges of experience in the Netherlands&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;High Tech Campus as a driver of innovation &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Combined economic, scientific and technological mission to Germany&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Exchange of know-how on the topic of energy efficiency &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New basis for an initiative dating back over 40 years&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Switzerland confirms membership in COST research network &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;International conference on the future of space research&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Cooperation as an essential prerequisite for success &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Copernicus, Europe‘s Global Monitoring for Environment and Security system:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;first satellite now in orbit&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>medien@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
      <link id="121576">
        <title>SERI News April 14</title>
        <uri>http://www.sbfi.admin.ch/aktuell/00399/01776/index.html?lang=en</uri>
        <position>Context</position>
      </link>
      <revisions> </revisions>
